**how —** Crystallized from Blaster Master (NES 1988) / Chō Wakusei Senki Metafight (1988).

**◌ the mythos —** It is the machine made a character: a tank you grow into a god, climbing walls and diving seas it could not at the start. a being of the subterranean war and the tank SOPHIA

